  "texts": [
    "One potential method to enforce this transparency is by introducing an audit mechanism when deploying these XAI algorithms.",
    "Decision-makers could only provide one or a limited number of explanations to the decision subject in this case.",
    "However, they would need to document and submit the reasoning, that led to the deployment of these XAI algorithms, for review to a third party.",
    "This entity would then evaluate whether the interests of the decision subject have been appropriately considered.",
    "However, this oversight should not be confined to the selection of the XAI algorithm alone."
  ],
